# Workspace Layout

This Cursor workspace contains several sibling git repositories. Do not assume
the workspace root is a git repo. Before git operations, read
`../space-setup/README.md` and run git commands from the relevant child repo,
for example `cadgenbench/`, `cadgenbench-data-gt/`, `space-setup/`, or
`cadgenbench-leaderboard/`.
